======================================== scoped_ptr tests ================================================================
FileManager open aimer.txt
node open aimer.txt
======================================== shared_ptr tests ================================================================
FileManager open shared_ptr ---> kylin_zhang 
node open shared_ptr ---> kylin_zhang 
FileManager open shared_ptr ----> naruto 
node open shared_ptr ----> naruto 
======================================== destructor call ================================================================
 next you will see , before the end of the program scoped_ptr will call the corresponding destruct methods
release node_t shared_ptr ----> naruto 
release FileManager shared_ptr ----> naruto 
release node_t shared_ptr ---> kylin_zhang 
release FileManager shared_ptr ---> kylin_zhang 
release node_t aimer.txt
release FileManager aimer.txt
